 the remaining AI words run out, automatic translation through TranslatePress AI will be paused.'=>'一旦剩余的 AI 字数用完，通过 TranslatePress AI 进行的自动翻译将会暂停。','To continue translating your content, please %1$s over at %2$s'=>'要继续翻译您的内容，请在 %2$s %1$s','Manage Notification: %s'=>'管理通知：%s','There is a new version of %1$s available. %2$sView version %3$s details%4$s or %5$supdate now%6$s.'=>'新版本 %1$s 可用。 %2$s 查看版本 %3$s 详细信息 %4$s 或者 %5$s 现在更新 %6$s。','There is a new version of %1$s available. %2$sView version %3$s details%4$s.'=>'新版本 %1$s 已经准备好了， %2$s 查看版本 %3$s 详细信息 %4$s。','To enable updates, please %1$senter your license key%2$s. Need a license key? %3$sPurchase one now%4$s.'=>'要启用更新，请%1$s输入您的许可证密钥%2$s。需要许可证密钥？%3$s立即购买%4$s。','To enable updates, please go to the %1$slicense page%2$s and check that you have a valid license.'=>'要启用更新，请前往%1$s许可证页面%2$s并确认您拥有有效的许可证。','To enable updates, your licence needs to be renewed. Please go to the %1$sTranslatePress Account%2$s page and login to renew.'=>'要启用更新，您的许可证需要续期。请前往%1$sTranslatePress Account%2$s页面并登录以续期。','You do not have permission to install plugin updates'=>'您无权安装插件更新','Error'=>'错误','Your TranslatePress license key is invalid or missing.'=>'您的 TranslatePress 许可证密钥无效或缺失。','Your license key expired on %s.'=>'你的许可证将期于%s过。','Your license key has been disabled.'=>'您的许可证密钥已被禁用。','Your license key is disabled for this URL. Re-enable it from <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=wp-dashboard&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=license-deactivated">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> Manage Sites.'=>'您的许可证密钥已在此 URL 禁用。请从 <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=wp-dashboard&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=license-deactivated">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> 管理网站 重新启用。','<p><strong>License key mismatch.</strong> The license you entered doesn’t match the TranslatePress version you have installed.</p><p>Please check that you’ve installed the correct version for your license from your TranslatePress account.</p>'=>'<p><strong>许可证密钥不匹配。</strong>您输入的许可证与您安装的 TranslatePress 版本不符。</p><p>请从您的 TranslatePress 账户确认您已安装与许可证相对应的正确版本。</p>','If you have only the free plugin installed but added a paid license, please install the paid plugin from your TranslatePress account.'=>'如果您只安装了免费插件，但添加了付费许可证，请从您的 TranslatePress 账户安装付费插件。','Your license key has reached its activation limit.'=>'您的许可证密钥已达到其激活限制。','Upgrade your plan to add more sites. %1$sUpgrade now%2$s'=>'升级您的方案以添加更多网站。%1$s立即升级%2$s','This website is already activated under a free license. Each website can only use one free license.'=>'该网站已使用免费许可证激活。每个网站只能使用一个免费许可证。','An error occurred, please try again.'=>'出现错误，请重试。','You have successfully activated your license'=>'您已成功激活许可证','Others'=>'其他','Restrict by Language'=>'按语言限制','Exclude from Language'=>'从语言中排除','Restrict element to language'=>'将元素限制为语言','Show this element only in one language.'=>'仅在一种语言中显示此元素。','Enable translation'=>'启用翻译','Allow translation to the corresponding language only if the content is written in the default language.'=>'仅当内容是用默认语言编写时，才允许翻译为相应的语言。','Select language'=>'选择语言','Choose in which language to show this element.'=>'选择显示此元素的语言。','Exclude element from language'=>'从语言中排除元素','Exclude this element from specific languages.'=>'从特定语言中排除此元素。','Select languages'=>'选择语言','Choose from which languages to exclude this element.'=>'从中选择要排除此元素的语言。','This element will still be visible when you are translating your website through the Translation Editor.'=>'当您通过翻译编辑器翻译网站时，此元素仍将可见。','The content of this element should be written in the default language.'=>'此元素的内容应以默认语言编写。','<strong>TranslatePress</strong> encountered SQL errors. <a href="%s" title="View TranslatePress SQL Errors">Check out the errors</a>.'=>'<strong>TranslatePress</strong>遇到 SQL 错误。<a href="%s" title="View TranslatePress SQL Errors">查看错误</a>。','Automatic translation has been disabled.'=>'自动翻译已禁用。','Dismiss this notice.'=>'忽略此提示。','Logged errors'=>'记录的错误','These are the most recent 5 errors logged by TranslatePress:'=>'以下是TranslatePress记录的最新 5 个错误：','Yes'=>'是','Why are these errors occuring'=>'为什么会发生这些错误','If TranslatePress detects something wrong when executing queries on your database, it may disable the Automatic Translation feature in order to avoid any extra charging by Google/DeepL. Automatic Translation needs to be manually turned on, after you solve the issues.'=>'如果TranslatePress在数据库上执行查询时检测到错误，可能会禁用"自动翻译"功能，以避免 Google/DeepL 的任何额外费用。解决问题后，需要手动打开自动翻译。','The SQL errors detected can occur for various reasons including missing tables, missing permissions for the SQL user to create tables or perform other operations, problems after site migration or changes to SQL server configuration.'=>'检测到的 SQL 错误可能出于各种原因发生，包括缺少表、SQL 用户缺少创建表或执行其他操作的权限、此问题一般出现在站点迁移后或更改 SQL 服务器配置后。','What you can do in this situation'=>'在这种情况下您可以做些什么','Plan A.'=>'计划 A.','Go to Settings -> TranslatePress -> General tab and Save Settings. This will regenerate the tables using your current SQL settings. Check if no more errors occur while browsing your website in a translated language. Look at the timestamps of the errors to make sure you are not seeing the old errors. Only the most recent 5 errors are displayed.'=>'转到设置->翻译->常规选项卡中并保存设置，此操作将使用当前 SQL 设置重新生成表。使用已翻译的语言浏览网站，检查错误是否不再发生，查看错误的时间戳，以确保您没有看到旧错误，仅显示最新的 5 个错误。','Plan B.'=>'计划 B.','If your problem isn\'t solved, try the following steps:'=>'如果您的问题没有解决，请尝试以下步骤：','Create a backup of your database'=>'创建数据库备份','Create a copy of each translation table where you encounter errors. You can copy the table within the same database (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY for example) -- perform this step only if you want to keep the current translations'=>'在遇到错误时创建每个翻译表的副本。您可以在同一数据库中复制该表（例如，trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY）-仅在想要保留当前翻译的情况下执行此步骤','Remove the trouble tables by executing the DROP function on them'=>'通过执行故障表上的 DROP 函数来删除它们','Go to Settings -> TranslatePress -> General tab and Save Settings. This will regenerate the tables using your current SQL server.'=>'转到设置->翻译->常规选项卡中并保存设置，此操作将在您的 SQL 服务器上重新生成数据表。','Copy the relevant content from the duplicated tables (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY for example) in the newly generated table (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es) -- perform this step only if you want to keep the current translations'=>'从新生成的表 （trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY） 中的重复表（例如trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY）中复制相关 trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es内容 -- 仅当您想要保留当前翻译时，才执行此步骤','Test it to see if everything is working. If something went wrong, you can restore the backup that you\'ve made at the first step. Check if no more errors occur while browsing your website in a translated language. Look at the timestamps of the errors to make sure you are not seeing the old errors. Only the most recent 5 errors are displayed.'=>'测试一下，看看是否一切都在工作。如果出现问题，您可以恢复第一步所做的备份。在以翻译的语言浏览您的网站时，检查是否不再出现任何错误。查看错误的时间戳，以确保您没有看到旧错误。仅显示最近的 5 个错误。','Plan C.'=>'计划 C.','If your problem still isn\'t solved, try asking your hosting about your errors. The most common issue is missing permissions for the SQL user, such as the Create Tables permission.'=>'如果问题仍未解决，请就此错误咨询您的主机服务商。最常见的问题是 SQL 用户缺少权限，例如"创建表"权限。','Could not install. Try again from <a href="%s" >Plugins Dashboard.</a>'=>'无法安装。重试请通过 <a href="%s" >插件仪表盘。</a>','Active'=>'启用','Permission denied.'=>'权限不足。','Invalid nonce.'=>'随机数无效。','Settings scope unknown.'=>'设置范围未知。','Legacy disabled.'=>'旧版已禁用。','Language Switcher'=>'语言切换','Change language to %s'=>'将语言更改为%s','Automatic Translation'=>'自动翻译','DeepL'=>'DeepL','Unsupported languages'=>'不支持的语言','The selected automatic translation engine does not provide support for these languages.<br>You can still manually translate pages in these languages using the Translation Editor.'=>'所选的自动翻译引擎不支持这些语言。<br>您仍可以使用翻译编辑器手动翻译页面为这些语言。','API key validation failed.'=>'API 密钥验证失败。','API key verification was successful.'=>'API 密钥验证成功。','Please enter your Google Translate key.'=>'请输入您的 Google 翻译密钥。','Please enter your DeepL API key.