ePress 账户安装付费插件。','You have reached the activation limit for your <strong>%1$s</strong> license. <br/>Manage your active sites from %2$s your account %3$s.'=>'您已达到 <strong>%1$s</strong> 许可证的激活上限。<br/>请从 %2$s您的账户%3$s 管理您的活跃站点。','Your license is disabled for this URL. Re-enable it from <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=wp-dashboard&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=license-deactivated">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> Manage Sites.'=>'您的许可证已在此 URL 禁用。请从 <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=wp-dashboard&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=license-deactivated">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> 管理站点 重新启用。','%1$s automatic translation requires an active license. Please %2$srenew%3$s your license or purchase a new one %4$shere%5$s.'=>'%1$s 自动翻译需要有效的许可证。请 %2$s续订%3$s 您的许可证，或 %4$s在此处%5$s 购买新许可证。','Please %1$senter%2$s your license key to enable %3$s automatic translation.'=>'请 %1$s输入%2$s 您的许可证密钥以启用 %3$s 自动翻译。','You have less than 5,000 TranslatePress AI words remaining. To continue automatically translating your website, please %spurchase additional AI words at a discount from your account%s.'=>'您的 TranslatePress AI 剩余字数已不足 5,000。要继续自动翻译您的网站，请 %s从您的账户中以折扣价购买额外的 AI 字数%s。',' Error: '=>' 错误： ','This website is already activated under a free license. Each website can only use one free license. Please upgrade to a premium plan for more TranslatePress AI words from %1$s your account %2$s.'=>'此网站已使用免费许可证激活。每个网站只能使用一个免费许可证。请从 %1$s您的账户%2$s 升级到高级方案以获取更多 TranslatePress AI 字数。','You do not have a valid license for <strong>TranslatePress</strong>. %1$sGet one for free%2$s to get access to TranslatePress AI.'=>'您没有有效的 <strong>TranslatePress</strong> 许可证。%1$s免费获取一个%2$s，以使用 TranslatePress AI。','<strong>NEW:</strong> The <strong>Different Domain per Language</strong> add-on is here! Boost your global SEO and create a local experience with country-specific domains like .de or .fr. Upgrade to <a href="ht