This language will be used in different operations such as sending email to the user.'=>'选中此设置后，首选语言仍为上述所选语言，无法在前台进行更改。<br>该语言将用于不同的操作，如向用户发送电子邮件。','Hello! Seems like you\'ve been using <strong>TranslatePress</strong> for a while now to translate your website. That\'s awesome! '=>'您好！看来您已经使用 <strong>TranslatePress</strong> 翻译您的网站有一段时间了。真不错！ ','If you can spare a few moments to rate it on WordPress.org it would help us a lot (and boost my motivation).'=>'如果您能抽出一些时间在 WordPress.org 上给它评分，那将对我们有很大帮助（并增强我的动力）。','~ Razvan, developer of TranslatePress'=>'~ Razvan，TranslatePress 的开发者','Rate TranslatePress on WordPress.org plugin page'=>'在 WordPress.org 插件页面上评价 TranslatePress','Ok, I will gladly help!'=>'好的，我很乐意提供帮助！','No, thanks.'=>'不，谢谢。','Full Language Names'=>'语言全称','Short Language Names'=>'语言简称','Flags with Full Language Names'=>'标志+语言全称','Flags with Short Language Names'=>'标志+语言简称','Only Flags'=>'仅标志','Full Language Names No HTML'=>'完整语言名称 无 HTML','Bottom Right'=>'右下角','Bottom Left'=>'左下角','Top Right'=>'右上','Top Left'=>'左上','Dark'=>'深色','Light'=>'明亮','Deactivate'=>'停用','Activate'=>'启用','Invalid language code. Please try again.'=>'语言代码无效。请重试。','Language codes can contain only A-Z a-z 0-9 - _ characters. Check your language codes in TranslatePress General Settings.'=>'语言代码只能包含 A-Z a-z 0-9 - _ 字符。请在 TranslatePress 常规设置中检查您的语言代码。','Error! Duplicate URL slug values.'=>'错误！网址别名重复。','You cannot select two languages that have the same <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes" target="_blank">iso code</a> but different formalities because doing so will lead to duplicate <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/specialty/international/localized-versions" target="_blank">hreflang tags</a>.'=>'您不能选择两种具有相同<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes" target="_blank">iso 代码</a>但不同手续的语言，因为这样做会导致<a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/specialty/international/localized-versions" target="_blank">hreflang 标记</a>重复。','Duplicate 