mium addons, automatic updates and support.'=>'请购买新许可证，以继续访问 TranslatePress AI、高级插件、自动更新和支持。','Purchase a new license'=>'购买新许可证','Your %s license is <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">missing or invalid</span>.'=>'您的 %s 许可证<span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">缺失或无效</span>。','Please enter a valid license to get access to TranslatePress AI, premium addons, automatic updates and support. Need a license key? %1$sPurchase one now%2$s'=>'请输入有效许可证，以访问 TranslatePress AI、高级插件、自动更新和支持。需要许可证密钥？%1$s立即购买%2$s','Enter a valid license'=>'输入有效的许可证','Slugs'=>'别名','Meta Information'=>'元信息','String List'=>'字符串列表','Gettext Strings'=>'Gettext 字符串','Images'=>'图片','Videos'=>'视频','Audios'=>'音频','Dynamically Added Strings'=>'动态添加的字符串','Translation Editor'=>'翻译编辑器','Edit translations by visually selecting them on each site page'=>'在每个网站页面上可视化地选择翻译进行编辑','String Translation'=>'字符串翻译','Edit url slug translations, plugins and theme translation (emails, forms etc.)'=>'编辑 url slug 翻译、插件和主题翻译（电子邮件、表单等）','Current User'=>'当前用户','Logged Out'=>'注销','Translate Page'=>'翻译页面','Add a New Language'=>'添加新语言','Get a Free AI License'=>'获取免费 AI 许可证','Your License is Invalid'=>'您的许可证无效','Get More AI Words (%d left)'=>'获取更多 AI 字数（剩余 %d）','Opens post in the translation editor. Post must be saved as draft or published beforehand.'=>'在翻译编辑器中打开帖子。帖子必须事先保存为草稿或发布。','Security check'=>'安全检查','<strong>Warning:</strong> Some strings have possibly incorrectly encoded characters. This may result in breaking the queries, rendering the page untranslated in live mode. Consider revising the following strings or their method of outputting.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong> 某些字符串可能错误地编码了字符。这可能会导致中断查询，使页面在实时模式下未翻译。请考虑修改以下字符串或其输出方法。','TranslatePress data update'=>'TranslatePress数据更新','We need to update your translations database to the latest version.'=>'我们需要将您的翻译数据库更新为最新版本。','Updating will allow editing translations of localized text from plugins and theme. Existing translation will still work as expected.'=>'更新后可编辑插件和主题中本地化文本