guage %s...'=>'为语言%s清理原始元数据表…','Replacing original id NULL with value for language %s...'=>'用语言 %s 的值替换原始 id NULL...','Inserting gettext original strings for language %s...'=>'插入语言 %s 的 gettext 原始字符串...','Cleaning gettext original strings table for language %s...'=>'清理语言 %s 的 gettext 原始字符串表...','Updating gettext original string ids for language %s...'=>'更新语言 %s 的 gettext 原始字符串 id...','Migrating taxonomy and post type base slugs to new table structure...'=>'正在将分类法和文章类型基础别名迁移到新的表结构...','Migrating post slugs to new table structure for language %s...'=>'正在将文章别名迁移到语言 %s 的新表结构...','Migrating term slugs to new table structure for language %s...'=>'正在将术语 slug 迁移到语言 %s 的新表结构……','Finishing up...'=>'完成...','Database optimization did not complete successfully. We recommend restoring the original database or <a href="%s" >trying again.</a>'=>'数据库优化未成功完成。建议还原原始数据库或 <a href="%s" >重试。</a>','Update aborted! Your user account doesn\'t have the capability to perform database updates.'=>'更新已中止！您的用户帐户无法执行数据库更新。','Update aborted! Invalid nonce.'=>'更新已中止！无效的 nonce 。','Update aborted! Incorrect action.'=>'更新已中止！操作不正确。','Update aborted! Incorrect language code.'=>'更新已中止！语言代码不正确。','Updating database to version %s+'=>'将数据库更新为版本 %s+','Processing table for language %s...'=>'为语言%s处理数据表...','Back to TranslatePress Settings'=>'返回 TranslatePress 设置','Successfully updated database!'=>'已成功更新数据库！',' done.'=>' 完成。','All individual TranslatePress add-on plugins <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">have been discontinued</a> and are now included in the premium Personal, Business and Developer versions of TranslatePress. Please log into your <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">account page</a>, download the new premium version and install it. Your individual addons settings will be ported over.'=>'所有单独的TranslatePress附加插件 <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">都已停产</a> ，现在包含在TranslatePress的高级个人，商业和开发人员版本中。请登录 <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">您的帐户页面</a>，下载新的高级版本并安装。您的个人插件设置将被移植过来。','Brand-new Language Switcher Settings are here!'=>'全新的语言切换器设置来了！','Explore pre-made templates, switch colors, flag styles, spacing, layouts & more. Use the live preview to perfect your switcher in seconds.'=>'探索预设模板，切换颜色、旗帜样式、间距、布局等。使用实时预览，在数秒内完善你的切换器。','Start customizing'=>'开始自定义','Read documentation'=>'阅读文档','TranslatePress'=>'TranslatePress','<strong>TranslatePress</strong> requires <strong><a href="http://php.net/manual/en/book.mbstring.php">Multibyte String PHP library</a></strong>. Please contact your server administrator to install it on your server.'=>'<strong>TranslatePress</strong>需要 <strong><a href="http://php.net/manual/en/book.mbstring.php">Multibyte String PHP 库</a></strong>才能工作，请联系您的服务器管理员安装。','Detected long query limitation on WPEngine hosting. Some large pages may appear untranslated. You can remove limitation by adding the following to your site’s wp-config.php: define( \'WPE_GOVERNOR\', false ); '=>'检测到 WPEngine 托管的长查询限制。一些大型页面可能会出现未翻译的情况。您可以在网站的 wp-config.php 中添加以下内容来消除限制： define( \'WPE_GOVERNOR\', false )； ','Custom Language Flag'=>'自定义语言标志','The Language code of the added custom language cannot be empty.'=>'添加的自定义语言的语言代码不能为空。','The Language code of the added custom language is invalid.'=>'添加的自定义语言的语言代码无效。','The Automatic Translation Code of the added custom language is invalid.'=>'添加的自定义语言的自动翻译代码无效。','TranslatePress Add-ons'=>'翻译按增件','You must first purchase this version to have access to the addon %1$shere%2$s'=>'您必须首先购买此版本才能访问附加%1$s在那里%2$s','Please %1$senter your license%2$s key first, to activate this addon.'=>'请先%1$s输入你的许可证%2$s密钥，以激活此附加组件。','You need an active license to have access to the addon. Renew or purchase a new one %1$shere%2$s.'=>'你需要有效的许可证才能访问此附加组件。请在%1$s此处%2$s续订或购买新许可证。','Advanced Add-ons'=>'高级附加组件','These addons extend your translation plugin and are available in the Developer, Business and Personal plans.'=>'这些插件扩展了您的翻译插件，并在开发人员计划、商业计划和个人计划中提供。','SEO Pack'=>'SEO 包','SEO Pack (Legacy)'=>'SEO Pack（旧版）','SEO support for page slug, page title, description and facebook and twitter social graph information. The HTML lang attribute is properly set.'=>'SEO 支持页面、页面标题、描述、脸谱和推特社交图表信息。HTML 朗属性设置正确。','Multiple Languages'=>'多种语言','Add as many languages as you need for your project to go global. Publish your language only when all your translations are done.'=>'添加尽可能多的语言，您需要您的项目走向全球。只有在完成所有翻译后才发布您的语言。','Pro Add-ons'=>'专业附加组件','These addons extend your translation plugin and are available in the Business and Developer plans.'=>'这些附加组件扩展了您的翻译插件，并在商业计划和开发计划中提供。','DeepL Automatic Translation'=>'深度自动翻译','Automatically translate your website through the DeepL API.'=>'通过DeepL API自动翻译您的网站。','Prompts visitors to switch to their preferred language based on their browser settings or IP address and remembers the last visited language.'=>'根据访客的浏览器设置或 IP 地址提示其切换至首选语言，并记住上次访问的语言。','Translator Accounts'=>'翻译帐户','Create translator accounts for new users or allow existing users that are not administrators to translate your website.'=>'为新用户创建翻译帐户，或允许不是管理员的现有用户翻译您的网站。','Browse As User Role'=>'浏览为用户角色','Navigate your website just like a particular user role would. Really useful for dynamic content or hidden content that appears for particular users.'=>'像特定用户角色一样浏览您的网站。对于显示给特定用户的动态内容或隐藏内容，非常有用。','Navigation Based on Language'=>'基于语言的导航','Configure different menu items for different languages.'=>'为不同的语言配置不同的菜单项。','Different Domain per Language'=>'每种语言使用不同域名','Connect separate domains or subdomains to each of your translated versions. Strengthen your brand’s local identity and boost SEO performance for every language you support.'=>'为每个翻译版本连接独立的域名或子域名。强化品牌的本地形象，并提升所支持每种语言的 SEO 表现。','Recommended Plugins'=>'推荐插件','A short list of plugins you can use to extend your website.'=>'可用于扩展网站的插件的简短列表。','Profile Builder'=>'资料生成器','Capture more user information on the registration form with the help of Profile Builder\'s custom user profile fields and/or add an Email Confirmation process to verify your customers accounts.'=>'借助Profile Builder的自定义用户资料字段或添加电子邮件确认流程来验证您用户账户，在注册表单上获取更多用户信息。','Paid Member Subscriptions'=>'课程订阅系统','Accept user payments, create subscription plans and restrict content on your membership site.'=>'接受用户付款, 创建订阅计划并限制您的会员网站上的内容.','WP Webhooks Automator'=>'WP Webhooks Automator','Create no-code automations and workflows on your WordPress site. Easily connect your plugins, sites and apps together.'=>'在 WordPress 站点上创建无代码自动化和工作流。轻松将你的插件、站点和应用连接在一起。','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','TranslatePress Errors'=>'TranslatePress错误','There are no logged errors.'=>'没有记录的错误。','Change language'=>'切换语言','Website language selector'=>'网站语言选择器','WordPress Translation Plugin'=>'WordPress 翻译插件','Available languages'=>'可用语言','Language Switcher update notice'=>'语言切换器更新通知','Legacy language switcher is currently enabled'=>'旧版语言切换器当前已启用','We’ve upgraded the switcher for richer customization and a better user experience.<br>In order to use the new configurator, turn off <strong>Load legacy language switcher</strong>.'=>'我们已升级切换器，以实现更丰富的自定义和更好的用户体验。<br>若要使用新版配置器，请关闭<strong>加载旧版语言切换器</strong>。','Note: You can switch back anytime from <strong>Advanced Settings → <a href="%s">Troubleshooting</a></strong>.'=>'注意：您可以随时从<strong>高级设置 → <a href="%s">故障排除</a></strong>切换回来。','Enable the new switcher'=>'启用新版切换器','Your License Key is valid.'=>'您的许可证密钥有效。','Your License Key is invalid.'=>'您的许可证密钥无效。','Your License has expired.'=>'您的许可证已过期。','Deactivate License'=>'停用许可证','Add a license key'=>'添加许可证密钥','License Key'=>'许可证','Manage your license in your %1$s.'=>'在您的%1$s中管理您的许可证。','Account Page'=>'账户页面','Don’t have a TranslatePress AI License Key?'=>'还没有 TranslatePress AI 许可证密钥？','You can get one for %1$sfree%2$s, by creating a free account. It includes:'=>'通过创建免费账户，您可以%1$s免费%2$s获取一个。它包含：','Access to TranslatePress AI for instant automatic translations'=>'使用 TranslatePress AI 进行即时自动翻译','2000 AI words to translate automatically'=>'2000 个可自动翻译的 AI 字数','Get a free License Today'=>'立即获取免费许可证','Debug Information'=>'调试信息','Debug Data for License Checking'=>'许可证检查调试数据','Debug Data for License Activation'=>'许可证激活调试数据','Get more AI words and unlock all features with TranslatePress Pro.'=>'获取更多 AI 字数，并使用 TranslatePress Pro 解锁所有功能。','Upgrade now ↗'=>'立即升级 ↗','Already purchased a Premium version?'=>'已购买高级版本？','Go to your %1$s'=>'前往您的 %1$s','TranslatePress.com Account'=>'TranslatePress.com 账户','Download & Install the Pro plugin'=>'下载并安装 Pro 插件','Learn More'=>'了解更多','Get a translation volume estimate with a detailed breakdown per page'=>'获取翻译量估算，并查看每页的详细细分','Find how many translatable words are on your website'=>'了解您网站上的可翻译字数','Enable Automatic Translation'=>'启用自动翻译','To use <strong>DeepL</strong> for automatic translation, activate this Pro add-on from the <a href="%1$s" target="_self" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>.'=>'要使用 <strong>DeepL</strong> 进行自动翻译，请从 <a href="%1$s" target="_self" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>激活此 Pro 加载项。','<strong>DeepL</strong> automatic translation is available as a <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>.'=>'<strong>DeepL</strong>自动翻译可以通过<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>启用。','By upgrading you\'ll get access to all paid add-ons, premium support and help fund the future development of TranslatePress.'=>'通过升级，您可以访问所有付费附加组件、高级支持，并帮助为TranslatePress的未来发展提供资金。','Please note that DeepL API usage is paid separately. See <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL pricing information</a>.'=>'请注意，DeepL API 的使用是需要单独付费的。请参阅 <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL 定价信息</a>。','TranslatePress Pro Add-ons'=>'TranslatePress 专业版附加组件','Test API credentials'=>'测试 API 凭据','Check if the selected translation engine is configured correctly.'=>'检查所选的翻译引擎是否配置正确。','Alternative Engines'=>'替代引擎','Switch to TranslatePress AI'=>'切换至 TranslatePress AI','Integrate machine translation directly with your WordPress website.'=>'将机器翻译直接集成到您的 WordPress 网站。','More info'=>'更多信息','Choose which engine you want to use in order to %1$s automatically translate your website.'=>'选择要使用的引擎，以便%1$s自动翻译您的网站。','Automatic Translation Settings'=>'自动翻译设置','AI Words Low Notification'=>'AI 字数不足通知','Receive an email notification when your TranslatePress AI word count drops below the specified threshold.'=>'当您的 TranslatePress AI 字数低于指定阈值时，接收邮件通知。','This feature is only available when using the TranslatePress AI translation engine.'=>'此功能仅在使用 TranslatePress AI 翻译引擎时可用。','Notification Email'=>'通知邮箱','The email address where the low AI words notification will be sent.'=>'接收 AI 字数不足通知的电子邮件地址。','Word Threshold'=>'字数阈值','words'=>'词数','You will be notified when remaining AI words drop below this number.'=>'当剩余 AI 词数低于此数字时，您将收到通知。','Automatically Translate Slugs'=>'自动翻译鼻涕虫','Generate automatic translations of slugs for posts, pages and Custom Post Types.<br/>The slugs will be automatically translated starting with the second refresh of each page.'=>'为帖子、页面和自定义帖子类型生成鼻涕虫的自动翻译。<br/>从每页的第二次刷新开始，将自动翻译数据块。','This feature is only available in the paid version. Upgrade TranslatePress and unlock more premium features.'=>'此功能仅在付费版本中可用。升级 TranslatePress，解锁更多高级功能。','Requires <a href="%s" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank">SEO Pack Add-on</a> to be installed and activated.'=>'需要先安装并激活 <a href="%s" title="TranslatePress SEO Pack 附加组件文档" target="_blank">SEO Pack 附加组件</a>','Upgrade now'=>'立即升级','Block Crawlers'=>'阻止爬虫','Block crawlers from triggering automatic translations on your website.<br>This will not prevent crawlers from accessing this site\'s pages.'=>'阻止爬虫在您的网站上触发自动翻译。<br>这不会阻止爬虫访问本网站的页面。','Limit machine translation / characters per day'=>'限制机器翻译每天的字符数','Add a limit to the number of automatically translated characters so you can better budget your project.'=>'对自动翻译的字符数添加限制，以便更好地为项目编制预算。','characters per day'=>'每日字符数','Today\'s Character Count: '=>'今日字符数： ','Log machine translation queries.'=>'记录机器翻译查询。','Only enable for testing purposes. Can impact performance.<br>All records are stored in the wp_trp_machine_translation_log database table. Use a plugin like <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a> to browse the logs or directly from your database manager (PHPMyAdmin, etc.)'=>'仅为测试目的启用。<br>所有记录都存储在 wp_trp_machine_translation_log 数据库表中。使用<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a>等插件或直接从数据库管理员（PHPMyAdmin 等）浏览日志。','Test API Credentials'=>'测试 API 凭据','HTTP Referrer: '=>'HTTP Referrer： ','Use this HTTP Referrer if the API lets you restrict key usage from its Dashboard.'=>'如果API允许您在其仪表板中的限制密钥使用，请使用此 HTTP Referrer。','Response'=>'响应','Response Body'=>'响应正文','Entire Response From wp_remote_get():'=>'来自wp_remote_get()的响应：','All Languages'=>'所有语言','Select the languages you wish to make your website available in.'=>'选择您希望使您的网站可用的翻译语言。','Formality'=>'礼节','Code'=>'代码','Slug'=>'别名','Default'=>'默认','Formal'=>'正式','Informal'=>'样式1','Language'=>'语言','This language does not support formality. '=>'该语言不支持正式程度。 ','Are you sure you want to remove this language?'=>'你确定要删除这个语言吗？','Custom Languages'=>'自定义语言','To Add more languages activate the Multiple Languages Addon'=>'要添加更多语言，请激活多语言附加组件','You need an active license to add more languages. Verify in your %1$saccount%2$s that your license is valid'=>'您需要有效的许可证才能添加更多语言。请在您的 %1$s账户%2$s 中验证许可证是否有效','Please %1$senter your license%2$s key first to add more languages.'=>'请先%1$s输入您的许可证%2$s密钥以添加更多语言','Adding more than two languages is a paid feature. Upgrade TranslatePress and unlock more premium features.'=>'添加超过两种语言是付费功能。升级 TranslatePress，解锁更多高级功能。','Website Languages'=>'网站语言','Default Language'=>'默认语言','Select the language your content is written in.'=>'选择您内容所使用的语言。','WARNING. Changing the default language will invalidate existing translations.'=>'警告。更改默认语言将使现有翻译无效。','Even changing from en_US to en_GB, because they are treated as two different languages.'=>'即使从en_US 到 en_GB，因为它们被视为两种不同的语言。','In most cases changing the default flag is all it is needed: '=>'在大多数情况下，需要更改默认标志： ','replace the default flag'=>'替换默认标志','Re-run Setup Wizard'=>'重新运行设置向导','The Setup wizard allows you to quickly setup TranslatePress. You can initiate it at any time.'=>'设置向导可帮助您快速设置 TranslatePress。您可以随时启动它。','Language Settings'=>'语言设置','Use Native language name'=>'使用本地语言名称','Check if you want to display languages in their native names. Otherwise, languages will be displayed in English.'=>'勾选此项以使用本地语言名称显示语言。否则，语言将以英语显示。','Use a subdirectory for the default language'=>'为默认语言使用子目录','Check if you want to add the subdirectory in the URL for the default language.</br>By checking this option, the default language seen by website visitors will become the first one in the "All Languages" list.'=>'勾选此项以为默认语言在 URL 中添加子目录。</br>勾选此项后，网站访客看到的默认语言将变为“所有语言”列表中的第一项。','Force language in custom links'=>'自定义链接中的强制语言','Select Yes if you want to force custom links without language encoding to keep the currently selected language.'=>'如果您想强制没有语言编码的自定义链接保留当前选定的语言，请选择是。','Shortcode '=>'短代码 ','Use shortcode on any page or widget.'=>'在任意页面或小工具中使用短代码。','You can also add the <a href="%s" title="Language Switcher Block Documentation">Language Switcher Block</a> in the WP Gutenberg Editor.'=>'您还可以在 WP Gutenberg 编辑器中添加<a href="%s" title="Language Switcher Block Documentation">语言切换器区块</a>。','Menu item'=>'菜单项','Go to  %1$s Appearance -> Menus%2$s to add languages to the Language Switcher in any menu.'=>'转到 %1$s 外观 -> 菜单%2$s 将语言切换工具添加到任一菜单中。','Learn more in our documentation.'=>'请在我们的文档中了解更多信息。','Floating language selection'=>'浮动语言选择框','Add a floating dropdown that follows the user on every page.'=>'在每一页上添加跟随用户的浮动下拉菜单。','Show "Powered by TranslatePress"'=>'显示 "Powered by TranslatePress"','Show the small "Powered by TranslatePress" label in the floater language switcher.'=>'在浮动器语言切换器中显示一个小小的"Powered by TranslatePress"标签。','5 Days to Better Multilingual Websites'=>'5天更好的多语言网站','%sJoin our FREE & EXCLUSIVE onboarding course%s and learn how to grow your multilingual traffic, reach international markets, and save time & money while getting the most out of TranslatePress!'=>'%s加入我们的免费和独家入职课程%s并学习如何增加您的多语言流量，进入国际市场，节省时间和金钱，同时充分利用TranslatePress！','Invalid email address'=>'无效的邮件地址','Your email'=>'您的邮箱','Sign me up!'=>'记住我！','Sign up with your email address and receive a 5-part email guide to help you maximize the power of TranslatePress.'=>'使用您的电子邮件地址注册，即可收到由 5 部分组成的电子邮件指南，帮助您最大限度地发挥 TranslatePress 的威力。','Dismiss email course notification'=>'关闭电子邮件课程通知','Hey %s,<br>Never miss an important update - opt in to our security and feature updates notifications, and non-sensitive diagnostic tracking.'=>'Hey%s,<br>千万不要错过重要更新 - 选择加入我们的安全和功能更新通知以及非敏感诊断跟踪。','Allow & Continue'=>'允许并继续','Skip'=>'跳过','This will allow TranslatePress to:'=>'这将允许 TranslatePress：','Your profile overview'=>'您的个人资料概述','Name and email address'=>'名称和电子邮件地址','Admin Notices'=>'管理员注意事项','Updates, announcements, marketing, no spam'=>'更新、公告、营销、无垃圾邮件','Plugin status & settings'=>'插件状态和设置','Active, Deactivated, installed version and settings'=>'激活、停用、安装版本和设置','Privacy Policy'=>'隐私政策','Terms of Service'=>'服务条款','Support'=>'支持','Documentation'=>'文档','Add Extra AI Words'=>'添加额外 AI 字数','Optimize TranslatePress database tables'=>'优化 TranslatePress 数据库表','<strong>IMPORTANT NOTE:</strong> Before performing this action it is strongly recommended to first backup the database.'=>'<strong>重要提示：</strong>执行此操作前，强烈建议先备份数据库。','IMPORTANT: It is strongly recommended to first backup the database!! Are you sure you want to continue?'=>'重要提示：强烈建议您先备份数据库！确实要继续吗？','Operations to perform'=>'要执行的操作','Remove CDATA for original and dictionary strings'=>'删除原始字符串和字典字符串的 CDATA','Removes CDATA from trp_original_strings and trp_dictionary_* tables.<br>This type of content should not be detected by TranslatePress. It might have been introduced in the database in older versions of the plugin.'=>'从 trp_original_strings 和 trp_dictionary_* 表中删除 CDATA。<br>TranslatePress 不应检测到这种类型的内容。这可能是旧版本插件在数据库中引入的。','Remove untranslated links from dictionary tables'=>'从字典表中删除未翻译的链接','Removes untranslated links and images from all trp_dictionary_* tables. These tables contain translations for user-inputted strings such as post content, post title, menus etc.'=>'删除所有 trp_dictionary_* 表中未翻译的链接和图片。这些表包含用户输入字符串的翻译，如帖子内容、帖子标题、菜单等。','Remove duplicate rows for gettext strings'=>'删除 gettext 字符串的重复行','Cleans up all trp_gettext_* tables of duplicate rows. These tables contain translations for themes and plugin strings.'=>'清理所有trp_gettext_* 表中的重复行。这些表包含主题和插件字符串的翻译。','Remove duplicate rows for dictionary strings'=>'删除字典字符串的重复行','Cleans up all trp_dictionary_* tables of duplicate rows. These tables contain translations for user-inputted strings such as post content, post title, menus etc.'=>'清理所有trp_dictionary_* 表中的重复行。这些表包含用户输入字符串的翻译，例如帖子内容、帖子标题、菜单等。','Remove duplicate rows for original dictionary strings'=>'删除原始字典字符串的重复行','Cleans up all trp_original_strings table of duplicate rows. This table contains strings in the default language, without any translation.<br>The trp_original_meta table, which contains meta information that refers to the post parent’s ID, is also regenerated.<br>Such duplicates can appear in exceptional situations of unexpected behavior.'=>'清理 trp_original_strings 表中的所有重复行。该表包含默认语言的字符串，没有任何翻译。<br>trp_original_meta 表（包含指向父文章 ID 的元信息）也将重新生成。<br>在出现意外行为的异常情况下，可能会产生此类重复。','Replace gettext strings that have original ID NULL with the correct original IDs'=>'将 original ID 为 NULL 的 gettext 字符串替换为正确的 original ID','Fixes an edge case issue where some gettext strings have the original ID incorrectly set to NULL, causing problems in the Translation Editor.<br>This operation corrects the original IDs in the trp_gettext_* tables.<br>Only check this option if you encountered an issue in the Translation Editor where clicking the green pencil did not bring up the gettext string for translation in the left sidebar.<br>Otherwise, please leave this option unchecked because it\'s an intensive operation.'=>'修复某些 gettext 字符串的 original ID 被错误设置为 NULL 的边界情况问题，该问题会导致翻译编辑器出现故障。<br>此操作会修正 trp_gettext_* 表中的 original ID。<br>仅在您遇到翻译编辑器中的以下问题时勾选此选项：点击绿色铅笔后，左侧边栏未显示可供翻译的 gettext 字符串。<br>否则，请保持此选项未勾选，因为这是一个资源密集型操作。','Optimize Database'=>'优化数据库','TranslatePress Database Updater'=>'TranslatePress数据库更新程序','Updating TranslatePress tables. Please leave this window open.'=>'正在更新 TranslatePress 数据表。请保持此窗口打开。','The inactive languages will still be visible and active for the admin. For other users they won\'t be visible in the language switchers and won\'t be accessible either.'=>'非活跃语言对管理员仍然可见且可用。对于其他用户，它们不会显示在语言切换器中，也无法访问。','unknown'=>'未知','<strong>Extra Languages add-on</strong> requires TranslatePress version %1$s or higher. You are currently using version %2$s. Please update TranslatePress to enable this feature.'=>'<strong>Extra Languages 附加组件</strong>需要 TranslatePress %1$s 或更高版本。您当前使用的是 %2$s 版本。请更新 TranslatePress 以启用此功能。','Automatic and manual slug translation changes performed when <strong>TranslatePress - Multilingual</strong> 2.8.4 was active had to be removed because of some issues with that version. All slug translations from before that version are now in use. Thank you for understanding!'=>'由于该版本存在一些问题，必须移除在 <strong>TranslatePress - Multilingual</strong> 2.8.4 激活期间执行的自动和手动 slug 翻译更改。该版本之前的所有 slug 翻译现已恢复使用。感谢您的理解！','If you absolutely need them, the removed translations can be found in tables trp_slug_original_obsolete and trp_slug_translation_obsolete.'=>'如果您确实需要这些翻译，可以在 trp_slug_original_obsolete 和 trp_slug_translation_obsolete 表中找到被移除的内容。','View Docs'=>'查看文档','Assign different domains or subdomains to each language. When visitors access these domains, TranslatePress loads the appropriate language translation directly without redirecting.'=>'为每种语言分配不同的域名或子域名。当访客访问这些域名时，TranslatePress 会直接加载相应的语言翻译，无需重定向。','Example: %1$s for English, %2$s for Spanish, %3$s for French.'=>'示例：%1$s 用于英语，%2$s 用于西班牙语，%3$s 用于法语。','Before enabling:'=>'启用前：','Ensure your domains are registered, pointed to your server, and have SSL certificates configured.'=>'确保您的域名已注册、指向您的服务器，并且已配置 SSL 证书。','Domain'=>'域名','Map this language to a different domain or sub-domain.'=>'将此语言映射到不同的域名或子域名。','https://example.com'=>'https://example.com','Prefill with current domain'=>'使用当前域名预填充','Check DNS'=>'检查 DNS','Checking DNS...'=>'正在检查 DNS...','DNS is correctly configured!'=>'DNS 配置正确！','DNS check failed. Please verify your domain configuration.'=>'DNS 检查失败。请验证您的域名配置。','This domain is already assigned to another language.'=>'该域名已分配给另一种语言。','<strong>Different Domain per Language add-on</strong> requires TranslatePress version %1$s or higher. You are currently using version %2$s. Please update TranslatePress to enable this feature.'=>'<strong>按语言分配不同域名附加组件</strong>需要 TranslatePress 版本 %1$s 或更高。您当前使用的版本是 %2$s。请更新 TranslatePress 以启用此功能。','Note: This option is disabled when Different Domain for Language addon is active.'=>'注意：当按语言分配不同域名附加组件处于活动状态时，此选项将被禁用。','Different Domain per Language: Domain is required when domain mapping is enabled. The toggle has been disabled for languages with empty domains.'=>'按语言分配不同域名：启用域名映射时，必须填写域名。已为空域名的语言禁用切换开关。','Different Domain per Language: The same domain cannot be assigned to multiple languages. The toggle has been disabled for duplicate domains.'=>'按语言分配不同域名：同一域名不能分配给多种语言。已为重复域名禁用切换开关。','Different Domain per Language: A language domain cannot be the same as the main site URL. The toggle has been disabled for the matching domain.'=>'按语言分配不同域名：语言域名不能与主站点 URL 相同。已为匹配的域名禁用切换开关。','Please enter a domain.'=>'请输入域名。','Invalid domain format.'=>'域名格式无效。','Could not reach domain: %s'=>'无法访问域名：%s','Domain returned HTTP status %d.'=>'域名返回 HTTP 状态 %d。','Domain is reachable!'=>'域名可访问！','Limit this menu item to the following languages'=>'将此菜单项限制为以下语言','Date format'=>'日期格式','Customize the date formatting per each translated language.<br/>Leave empty for default WP setting or see more information <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/" title="Formatting Date and Time" target="_blank">here</a>'=>'为每种翻译语言设置自定义日期格式。<br/>留空使用WP默认设置，或<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/" title="Formatting Date and Time" target="_blank">在此</a>查看更多信息','To edit an existing TranslatePress language, input the language code and fill in only the columns you want to overwrite (e.g. Language name, Flag).<br>You can also add new custom languages. They will be available under General settings, All Languages list, where the URL slug can be edited.'=>'若要编辑现有的 TranslatePress 语言，请输入语言代码，并仅填写您想要覆盖的列（例如语言名称、国旗）。<br>您还可以添加新的自定义语言。它们将在常规设置的“所有语言”列表中可用，您可以在其中编辑 URL slug。','For custom flag, first upload the image in media library then paste the URL.<br>Changing or deleting a custom language will impact translations and site URL\'s.<br>The Language code and the ISO Code should contain only alphabetical values, numerical values, "-" and "_".<br>The ISO Codes can be found on <a href = "https://cloud.google.com/translate/docs/languages" target = "_blank">Google ISO Codes</a> and <a href = "https://www.deepl.com/docs-api/translating-text/" target = "_blank">DeepL Target Codes</a>.'=>'如需使用自定义国旗图标，请先将图片上传至媒体库，然后粘贴 URL。<br>更改或删除自定义语言将影响翻译和网站 URL。<br>语言代码和 ISO 代码只能包含字母、数字、“-”和“_”。<br>ISO 代码可在 <a href = "https://cloud.google.com/translate/docs/languages" target = "_blank">Google ISO 代码</a> 和 <a href = "https://www.deepl.com/docs-api/translating-text/" target = "_blank">DeepL 目标代码</a> 页面查看。','Language code'=>'语言代码','Language name'=>'语言名称','Native name'=>'母语名称','ISO Code'=>'ISO 代码','Flag URL'=>'国旗URL','Text RTL'=>'文本 RTL','Custom language'=>'自定义语言','Disable dynamic translation'=>'禁用动态翻译','It disables detection of strings displayed dynamically using JavaScript. <br/>Strings loaded via a server side AJAX call will still be translated.'=>'此项禁止使用JavaScript动态显示字符串的检测。<br/>通过服务器端Ajax调用加载的字符串仍将被翻译。','Disable translation for gettext strings'=>'禁用 gettext 字符串的翻译','Gettext Strings are strings outputted by themes and plugins. <br> Translating these types of strings through TranslatePress can be unnecessary if they are already translated using the .po/.mo translation file system.<br>Enabling this option can improve the page load performance of your site in certain cases. The disadvantage is that you can no longer edit gettext translations using TranslatePress, nor benefit from automatic translation on these strings.'=>'Gettext 字符串是由主题和插件输出的字符串。 <br> 如果这些字符串已经使用 .po/.mo 翻译文件系统进行了翻译，则无需通过 TranslatePress 翻译这些类型的字符串。<br>在某些情况下，启用此选项可以提高网站的页面加载性能。缺点是您不能再使用 TranslatePress 编辑 gettext 翻译，也不能受益于这些字符串的自动翻译。','Gettext Strings translation is disabled'=>'已禁用 Gettext 字符串翻译','To enable it go to '=>'要启用该功能，请访问 ','TranslatePress->Advanced Settings->Debug->Disable translation for gettext strings'=>'TranslatePress->高级设置->调试->禁用 Gettext 字符串翻译',' and uncheck the Checkbox.'=>' 并取消选中复选框。','Dismiss'=>'忽略','Exclude translated links from sitemap'=>'从站点地图中排除已翻译的链接','Do not include translated links in sitemaps generated by SEO plugins.<br/>Requires <a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=miscellaneous" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank"> SEO Pack Add-on</a> to be installed and activated.'=>'不要在 SEO 插件生成的 sitemaps 中包含翻译后的链接。<br/>需要安装并激活<a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=miscellaneous" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank"> SEO Pack 附加组件</a>。','Disable post container tags for post title'=>'禁用文章标题的文章容器标签','It disables search indexing the post title in translated languages.<br/>Useful when the title of the post doesn\'t allow HTML thus breaking the page.'=>'此选项禁止搜索引擎索引此语言版本的文章标题。<br/>当文章标题不允许 HTML 从而破坏页面时非常有用。','Disable post container tags for post content'=>'禁用文章内容的文章容器标签','It disables search indexing the post content in translated languages.<br/>Useful when the content of the post doesn\'t allow HTML thus breaking the page.'=>'此选项禁止搜索引擎索引此语言版本的文章内容。<br/>当文章内容不允许 HTML 从而破坏页面时非常有用。','Do not translate certain paths'=>'不要翻译某些路径','Choose what paths can be translated. Supports wildcard at the end of the path.<br>For example, to exclude https://example.com/some/path you can either use the rule /some/path/ or /some/*.<br>Enter each rule on it\'s own line. To exclude the home page use {{home}}.'=>'选择可以转换的路径。在路径末尾支持通配符。<br>例如，要排除https://example.com/some/path，可以使用规则 /some/path/ 或 /some/ *。<br>输入每个自己行。要排除主页，请使用{{home}}。','Exclude Paths From Translation'=>'从翻译中排除路径','Translate Only Certain Paths'=>'仅翻译某些路径','Enable the hreflang x-default tag for language:'=>'为语言启用 hreflang x-default 标记：','Enables the hreflang="x-default" for an entire language. See documentation for more details.'=>'启用所有语言的 hreflang="x-default"。有关详细信息，请参阅文档。','Translate numbers and numerals'=>'翻译数字和数字','Enable translation of numbers ( e.g. phone numbers)'=>'启用数字翻译（例如电话号码）','Selector'=>'选择器','Exclude from dynamic translation'=>'从动态翻译中排除','Do not dynamically translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being translated using JavaScript.<br/>These strings will still be translated on the server side if possible.'=>'不要动态转换在与这些选择器匹配的html节点中找到的字符串。<br>排除与这些选择器匹配的所有HTML节点的子级，不使用JavaScript进行转换。<br/>如果可能，仍在服务器端转换这些字符串。','Gettext String'=>'获取文本字符串','Exclude Gettext Strings'=>'排除Gettext字符串','Exclude these strings from being translated as Gettext strings by TranslatePress. Leave the domain empty to take into account any Gettext string.<br/>Can still be translated through po/mo files.'=>'排除这些字符串，使其不被TranslatePress翻译为Gettext字符串，留空此项可翻译所有 Gettext 字符串。<br/>您仍可以通过 po/mo 文件进行翻译。','Exclude selectors only from automatic translation'=>'仅从自动翻译中排除选择器','Do not automatically translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being automatically translated.<br>Manual translation of these strings is still possible.'=>'不要自动翻译与这些选择器匹配的html节点中的字符串<br>排除自动翻译与这些选择器匹配的HTML节点的所有子节点<br>仍然可以手动翻译这些字符串。','Exclude selectors from translation'=>'从翻译中排除选择器','Do not translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being translated.<br>These strings cannot be translated manually nor automatically.'=>'不翻译匹配这些选择器的 HTML 节点中的字符串。<br>不翻译匹配这些选择器的 HTML 节点的所有子节点。<br>这些字符串既不能手动翻译，也不能自动翻译。','String'=>'字符串','Exclude strings from automatic translation'=>'从自动转换中排除字符串','Do not automatically translate these strings (ex. names, technical words...)<br>Paragraphs containing these strings will still be translated except for the specified part.'=>'不要自动翻译这些字符串（例如名称、技术词...）<br>包含这些字符串的段落仍将翻译，但指定的部分除外。','Fix broken HTML'=>'修复损坏的 HTML','General attempt to fix broken or missing HTML on translated pages.<br/>'=>'一般尝试修复翻译页面上损坏或缺失的 HTML。<br/>','Force slash at end of home url:'=>'在主页 url 末尾强制斜线：','Ads a slash at the end of the home_url() function'=>'在 home_url() 函数末尾添加斜杠','Show Both (recommended)'=>'同时显示两者（推荐）','Remove Country Locale'=>'删除国家/地区区域设置','Remove Region Independent Locale'=>'删除独立于区域的区域设置','Remove duplicate hreflang'=>'删除重复的 hreflang','Choose which hreflang tags will appear on your website.<br/>We recommend showing both types of hreflang tags as indicated by <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/advanced/crawling/localized-versions" title="Google Crawling" target="_blank">Google documentation</a>.<br/>Removing Country Locale when having multiple Country Locales of the same language (ex. English UK and English US) will result in showing one hreflang tag with link to just one of the region locales for that language.'=>'选择哪些 hreflang 标签将显示在您的网站上。<br/>我们建议按照 <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/advanced/crawling/localized-versions" title="Google Crawling" target="_blank">Google 文档</a> 的说明同时显示这两种 hreflang 标签。<br/>当同一语言存在多个国家/地区区域设置时（例如 English UK 和 English US），移除国家/地区区域设置将导致只显示一个 hreflang 标签，且该标签仅链接到该语言的某个区域设置。','Default (example: en-US, fr-CA, etc.)'=>'默认值（例如：en-US、fr-CA 等）','Regional (example: en, fr, es, etc.)'=>'区域（例如：英语、法语、西班牙语等）','HTML Lang Attribute Format'=>'HTML 郎属性格式','Change lang attribute of the html tag to a format that includes country regional or not. <br>In HTML, the lang attribute (<html lang="en-US">)  should be used to  specify the language of text content so that the  browser can correctly display or process  your content (eg. for  hyphenation, styling, spell checking, etc).'=>'将 html 标签的 lang 属性改为包含或不包含国家地区的格式。<br>在 HTML 中，应使用 lang 属性 (<html lang="en-US">) 指定文本内容的语言，以便浏览器能正确显示或处理您的内容（如连字符、样式、拼写检查等）。','Load legacy Language Switcher'=>'加载旧版语言切换器','Applies to all types of language switchers (floating, shortcode, and menu). When enabled, the site will revert to using the original Language Switcher configured in the General Settings tab, replacing the new customizable version. Your existing switcher settings will remain saved, but they will be ignored while this option is active.'=>'适用于所有类型的语言切换器（浮动、shortcode 和菜单）。启用后，网站将恢复使用在“常规设置”选项卡中配置的原始语言切换器，以替代新的可自定义版本。您现有的切换器设置将保留，但在此选项启用期间将被忽略。','Load legacy SEO Pack Add-On'=>'加载旧版 SEO Pack 扩展','In case the recent migration to the new slug rewrite is causing trouble, set this to Yes to use the old method <br> Please <a href="https://translatepress.com/support/open-ticket/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=troubleshooting" target="_blank">open a support ticket</a> letting us know of the issues you are having.'=>'如果最近迁移到新的 slug 重写方式导致问题，请将此选项设为“是”以使用旧方法。<br>请<a href="https://translatepress.com/support/open-ticket/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=troubleshooting" target="_blank">提交支持工单</a>，告知我们您遇到的问题。','Manual Translation Only'=>'仅手动翻译','TranslatePress pro-actively scans and saves strings in the database when users access translated pages. <br>This setting disables this functionality and only allows translation and string saving when inside the Translation Editor. <br>Also disables machine translation outside the Translation Editor, giving you better control over character spending, by translating only the pages you visit in the Translation Editor.'=>'TranslatePress 会在用户访问已翻译页面时主动扫描并将字符串保存到数据库中。<br>此设置会禁用该功能，仅允许在翻译编辑器内进行翻译和字符串保存。<br>还会禁用翻译编辑器外部的机器翻译，让您通过仅翻译在翻译编辑器中访问的页面来更好地控制字符消耗。','Open language switcher only on click'=>'仅单击时打开语言切换器','Open the language switcher shortcode by clicking on it instead of hovering.<br> Close it by clicking on it, anywhere else on the screen or by pressing the escape key. This will affect only the shortcode language switcher.'=>'通过单击而不是悬停来打开语言切换器短代码。<br> 通过单击它，屏幕上的任何其他位置或按转义键来关闭它。这将仅影响短代码语言切换器。','Show opposite language in the language switcher'=>'在语言切换器中显示相反的语言','Transforms the language switcher into a button showing the other available language, not the current one.<br> Only works when there are exactly two languages, the default one and a translation one.<br>This will affect the shortcode language switcher and floating language switcher as well.<br> To achieve this in menu language switcher go to Appearance->Menus->Language Switcher and select Opposite Language.'=>'将语言切换器转换为显示其他可用语言（而不是当前语言）的按钮。<br> 仅当正好有两种语言（默认语言和翻译语言）时才有效。<br>这也会影响短代码语言切换器和浮动语言切换器。<br> 要在菜单语言切换器中实现此目的，请转到外观>菜单>语言切换器，然后选择“对应语言”。','<a href="%s">Click here</a> to access the database optimization tool.'=>'<a href="%s">单击此处</a>访问数据库优化工具。','It helps remove possible duplicate translations, clear unnecessary data and repair possible metadata issues.'=>'它有助于删除可能存在的重复翻译、清除不必要的数据并修复可能存在的元数据问题。','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Here</a> you can observe the last 5 SQL errors relevant to TranslatePress if they exist.'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank">此处</a> 可查看与 TranslatePress 相关的最近 5 条 SQL 错误（如有）。','Troubleshooting'=>'故障排除','Exclude Gettext strings'=>'排除 Gettext 字符串','Debug'=>'调试','Custom languages'=>'自定义语言','Miscellaneous options'=>'其他选项','Exclude strings & pages'=>'排除字符串和页面','Automatic Translation Memory'=>'自动翻译记忆','Serve same translation for similar text. The strings need to have a percentage of 95% similarity.<br>Helps prevent losing existing translation when correcting typos or making minor adjustments to the original text. <br>If a translation already exists for a very similar original string, it will automatically be used for the current original string.<br>Does not work when making changes to a text that is part of a translation block unless the new text is manually merged again in a translation block.<br>Each string needs to have a minimum of 50 characters.'=>'为相似文本提供相同翻译。字符串需要具有95%的相似度。<br>有助于在纠正拼写错误或对原始文本进行微调时防止丢失现有翻译。 <br>如果已存在与非常相似的原始字符串对应的翻译，则将自动用于当前的原始字符串。<br>对属于翻译块的文本进行更改时无效，除非新文本被手动重新合并到翻译块中。<br>每个字符串至少需要50个字符。','WARNING: This feature can negatively impact page loading times in secondary languages, particularly with large databases (for example websites with a lot of pages or products). If you experience slow loading times, disable this and try again.'=>'警告：此功能可能会对次要语言的页面加载时间产生负面影响，尤其是在数据库较大时（例如包含大量页面或产品的网站）。如果您遇到加载缓慢的情况，请禁用此功能后重试。','Fix missing dynamic content'=>'修复缺少的动态内容','May help fix missing content inserted using JavaScript. <br> It shows dynamically inserted content in original language for a moment before the translation request is finished.'=>'可能有助于修复使用 JavaScript 插入的缺失内容。 <br> 在翻译请求完成之前，它会以原始语言动态显示插入的内容。','Filter Gettext wrapping from post content and title'=>'从文章内容和标题中过滤 Gettext 包裹','Filters gettext wrapping such as #!trpst#trp-gettext from all updated post content and post title. Does not affect previous post content. <br/><strong>Database backup is recommended before switching on.</strong>'=>'从所有更新后的文章标题和内容中过滤gettext换行，如 #!trpst#trp-gettext，此操作不影响以前的文章内容。<br/><strong>建议在打开之前备份数据库。</strong>','Filter Gettext wrapping from post meta'=>'从文章元数据中过滤Gettext包裹','Filters gettext wrapping such as #!trpst#trp-gettext from all updated post meta. Does not affect previous post meta. <br/><strong>Database backup is recommended before switching on.</strong>'=>'从所有更新后的文章元数据中过滤gettext换行，如 #!trpst#trp-gettext，不影响上一个文章元数据。<br/><strong>建议在打开之前进行数据库备份。</strong>','Google Translate v2'=>'谷歌翻译 v2','Google Translate API Key'=>'谷歌翻译API密钥','Add your API Key here...'=>'在此处添加您的 API 密钥...','Visit <a href="https://cloud.google.com/docs/authentication/api-keys" target="_blank">this link</a> to see how you can set up an API key, <strong>control API costs</strong> and set HTTP referrer restrictions.'=>'点击<a href="https://cloud.google.com/docs/authentication/api-keys" target="_blank">这里</a>获取API key。<strong>控制API成本</strong>并设置HTTP referrer 限制。','Your HTTP referrer is: %s'=>'您的 HTTP referrer是： %s','There was an error on the server processing your Google Translate key.'=>'服务器在处理您的 Google 翻译密钥时出现错误。','There was an error with your Google Translate key.'=>'您的 Google 翻译密钥有误。','Please check your TranslatePress license key.'=>'请检查您的 TranslatePress 许可证密钥。','TranslatePress AI'=>'TranslatePress AI','No Active License Detected for this website.'=>'未检测到该网站的有效许可证。','In order to enable Automatic Translation using TranslatePress AI, you need a license key by creating a free account.'=>'若要使用 TranslatePress AI 启用自动翻译，您需要创建免费账户以获取许可证密钥。','Create your Free Account'=>'创建免费账户',' or '=>' 或 ','Enter your license key'=>'输入您的许可证密钥',' Or %1$spurchase one here%2$s'=>' 或 %1$s在此购买%2$s','Your free account includes: '=>'您的免费账户包含： ','Get more AI Words and unlock all AI features with TranslatePress Pro.'=>'获取更多 AI 字数，并使用 TranslatePress Pro 解锁所有 AI 功能。','You have a valid %s <strong>license</strong>.'=>'您拥有有效的 %s <strong>许可证</strong>。',' words remaining. '=>' 字剩余。 ','Recheck'=>'重新检查','Rechecking...'=>'正在重新检查…','Done.'=>'完成。','Manage your license & quota on the %s'=>'在 %s 上管理您的许可证和配额','TranslatePress.com Account Page'=>'TranslatePress.com 账户页面','SEO support for page slug, page title, description and Facebook and Twitter social graph information. The HTML lang attribute is properly set.'=>'为页面 slug、页面标题、描述以及 Facebook 和 Twitter 社交图谱信息提供 SEO 支持。HTML lang 属性会被正确设置。','Enable Modules'=>'启用模块','Enable Add-on modules to extend TranslatePress and enhance the functionality of your translated site.'=>'启用附加模块以扩展 TranslatePress，并增强翻译网站的功能。','More functionality with TranslatePress Pro.'=>'TranslatePress Pro 提供更多功能。','Already a Pro User?'=>'已是 Pro 用户？','Activate License Key'=>'激活许可证密钥','This add-on is not available on your current plan.'=>'此附加组件在您当前的套餐中不可用。','Continue'=>'继续','The link you followed has expired. Please reload the page and try again.'=>'您访问的链接已过期。请重新加载页面后重试。','A valid license is required to enable Automatic Translation.'=>'启用自动翻译需要有效的许可证。','Your license key is disabled for this URL. Re-enable it from <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=tp-onboarding&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=tp-ai">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> Manage Sites.'=>'您的许可证密钥已对此 URL 禁用。请从 <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=tp-onboarding&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=tp-ai">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> 管理站点 重新启用。','<p><strong>License key mismatch.</strong> The license you entered doesn\'t match the TranslatePress version you have installed.</p><p>Please check that you\'ve installed the correct version for your license from your TranslatePress account.</p>'=>'<p><strong>许可证密钥不匹配。</strong>您输入的许可证与您安装的 TranslatePress 版本不匹配。</p><p>请从您的 TranslatePress 账户中确认，您已安装与许可证对应的正确版本。</p>','Automatically translate your website using TranslatePress AI.'=>'使用 TranslatePress AI 自动翻译您的网站。','In order to enable Automatic Translation using TranslatePress AI, please enter your license key from'=>'要使用 TranslatePress AI 启用自动翻译，请输入您的许可证密钥，来自','your account.'=>'您的账户。','Skip and continue with manual translation »'=>'跳过并继续使用手动翻译 »','Get Your Free TranslatePress AI License'=>'获取免费的 TranslatePress AI 许可证','Generate License'=>'生成许可证','Creating a free account includes: '=>'创建免费账户包含： ','Are you a TranslatePress PRO user?'=>'您是 TranslatePress PRO 用户吗？','Install & Activate your pro plugin.'=>'安装并激活您的专业版插件。','Skip this step'=>'跳过此步骤','The 